import img1 from '../images/city1.jpg'
import img2 from '../images/desert1.webp'
import img3 from '../images/coffee.jpg'
import Carousel from '../components/Carousel'
import city from '../images/city2.jpg'
import forest from '../images/forest1.jpg'
import family from '../images/family1.webp'
import desert from '../images/desert1.webp'
import market from '../images/market1.jpg'
import sea from '../images/sea1.jpg'
import { Grid } from '@mui/material'
import CardRound from '../components/CardRound'
export default function HomePage(){
    
    const images=[
            {
                label:"city",
                img:img1
            },{
                label:"dessert",
                img:img2
            },{
                label:"coffee",
                img:img3
            }
        ]
    
    return <>
    <Carousel images={images} />
    <Grid container spacing={2}>
        <Grid item xs={4} md={4}>
            <CardRound image={sea} title={"sea"} text={"come to an extere sail on the red sea"} url={"/"}/>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={4} md={4}>
            <CardRound image={forest} title={"forest"} text={"a romantic meeting among the mysterious trees o fthe north"} url={"/"}/>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={4} md={4}>
            <CardRound image={city} title={"sea"} text={"come to an extere sail on the red sea"} url={"/"}/>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={4} md={4}>
            <CardRound image={market} title={"sea"} text={"come to an extere sail on the red sea"} url={"/"}/>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={4} md={4}>
            <CardRound image={family} title={"sea"} text={"come to an extere sail on the red sea"} url={"/"}/>
        </Grid>
        <Grid item xs={4} md={4}>
            <CardRound image={desert} title={"sea"} text={"come to an extere sail on the red sea"} url={"/"}/>
        </Grid>
    </Grid>
    </>
}
